# Implementation Plan - NanoMed React TMA Frontend

This plan outlines the creation of a professional React-based Telegram Mini App for the NanoMed clinic, featuring a visual booking system.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Dependencies**: I will install `lucide-react` for icons and `framer-motion` for smooth animations to ensure a premium look.
> **Deployment**: To use this in Telegram, the frontend needs to be hosted (e.g., Vercel/Netlify) and the URL must be set in the BotFather settings.

